Jolene Brand https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jolene_Brand 0 Jolene Brand (born Jolene Marie Bufkin; July 31, 1934, Los Angeles, California) is an American actress. She is married to George Schlatter and has two daughters – Andrea Justine Schlatter and Maria S. Schlatter. She acted most in the 1950s/60s, and appeared in a number of Ernie Kovacs television programs.
